title: Hong Kong GDP Deflator
description: GDP Deflator in Hong Kong increased to 105.80 points in the third quarter of 2022 from 101.30 points in the second quarter of 2022. GDP Deflator in Hong Kong averaged 64.81 points from 1973 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 105.80 points in the third quarter of 2022 and a record low of 12.80 points in the second quarter of 1973. This page provides - Hong Kong GDP Deflator - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Census and Statistics Department, Hong Kong
